				<h3>1. Middleware Approach</h3>
				<p>Create middleware that automatically optimizes all requests:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Intercept API calls before sending to AI models</li>
					<li>Apply optimization rules automatically</li>
					<li>Monitor and log optimization results</li>
					<li>Provide fallback mechanisms</li>
				</ul>

